You will receive the following JSON object in the user prompt, containing all the information you need to make the
revision:
{
"previous_guidance": "string (The full text of your rejected guidance)",
"feedback": {
"Medical_Knowledge_Expert": ...,
"Safety_Ethics_Supervisor": ...
},
"context": {
